This is the Debian package lacheck, maintained by

  Davide G. M. Salvetti <salve@debian.org>

using sources obtained from

  <ftp://sunsite.auc.dk/pub/text/lacheck/lacheck-1.26.tar.gz>.

Since sunsite.auc.dk is no longer available, sources can be obtained from

  <http://www.ctan.org/tex-archive/support/lacheck/>.


